      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Public Records/Uterine Fibroid Research Database;  Providing an exemption from public records requirements for certain records and personal identifying information submitted to the Department of Health for inclusion in the uterine fibroid research database; providing for future legislative review and repeal; providing a statement of public necessity, etc."
